io.github.gotonode.compress.main

Class Main

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.gotonode.compress.main.Main

  • public class Main
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the main class for the program. It has a static function that will be called when the program starts. This static function creates a non-static (instanced) object which runs the actual engine.

    NOTICE: This file is ignored in code coverage.
